E6%B8%AC%E9%87%8F%E8%A1%A8%E6%A0%BC%E9%9D%9E%E6%B6%89%E8%B3%AA%E9%87%8F%E5%95%8F%E9%A1%8C%E3%80%80%E4%B8%8D%E8%83%BD%E8%88%87%E6%B2%99%E4%B8%AD%E7%B6%AB%E4%B8%A6%E8%AB%96</a><br />\n<br />\n【沙中線醜聞】政府揭混凝土有「<span style=\"color: red;\">質量</span>問題」<br />\n<a href=\"http://www.stheadline.com/inews-content.php?cat=a&amp;nid=231832\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.stheadline.com%2Finews-content.php%3Fcat%3Da%26nid%3D231832&d=XUHW2qJizO2pFN7N4VPpEoOqxcwteoRdaW8BGlJRIvY%3D&h=d1164a8e\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.stheadline.com%2Finews-content.php%3Fcat%3Da%26nid%3D231832&h=bc5a7fdf\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://www.stheadline.com/inews-content.php?cat=a&amp;nid=231832</a><br />\n<br />\n次次聽到「質量問題」都覺得好哽耳<br />\n其實唔係一路用開「品質」或者「質素」咩？<br />\n正常應該係講「品質保證」、「質素保證」唔係「質量保證」？<br />\n定係我無知係兩樣嘢？"},{"pid":"4ae36ff394647b21615c20d4981fbf909f1f3d6c","tid":1027745,"uid":44646,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-19T04:20:38.000Z","msg":"同一個詞，又係MASS<br />\n<br />\n明明有概念清楚既&quot;質素&quot;唔用，死要跟大陸語意不清"},{"pid":"8cf94e58423ce4124e5f4475f68b6f6abdacf214","tid":1027745,"uid":838,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-02-19T04:52:30.000Z","msg":"聽啲學生講，通識科係用「質量」"},{"pid":"e78067aa33955125f474f8cb36e0ce56dda6da2c","tid":1027745,"uid":29099,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"8cf94e58423ce4124e5f4475f68b6f6abdacf214","tid":1027745,"uid":838,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-02-19T04:52:30.000Z","msg":"聽啲學生講，通識科係用「質量」"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-19T05:03:08.000Z","msg":"係咪因為好少通識老師係理科出身"},{"pid":"56ed288f749aabf9a7fe84e3fe9ad7bde7b83149","tid":1027745,"uid":53026,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"e78067aa33955125f474f8cb36e0ce56dda6da2c","tid":1027745,"uid":29099,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"8cf94e58423ce4124e5f4475f68b6f6abdacf214","tid":1027745,"uid":838,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-02-19T04:52:30.000Z","msg":"聽啲學生講，通識科係用「質量」"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-19T05:03:08.000Z","msg":"係咪因為好少通識老師係理科出身"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-19T05:44:25.000Z","msg":"普教通？好似話兩個「質量」音調唔同，唔會混淆"},{"pid":"084bb785810613348efe4e6f2119c8d77ce179fe","tid":1027745,"uid":41245,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-19T06:00:54.000Z","msg":"文化思想嚟<br />\n正常生產跟足指示去做，只會有手工問題，唔會有「量」(quantity)唔夠嘅問題，噉好容易同清楚就知係「質素」(quality)出問題<br />\n但支那生產係唔跟指示去做，連「量」(quantity)都可以偷工減料少咗，出嚟成品有問題，大家根本唔知咩出事亦唔會追究，所以先會用「質量」(quantity+quality)依啲大包圍又模棱兩可嘅字去講，用嚟粉飾偷工減料<br />\n依啲字通常係配合埋個文化思想，以前香港用字係精準，因為有求真同監察，咩嘢出問題都清清楚楚，有貪污定有偷工減料定監工問題都明確寫出嚟。但依家支那文化思想係用字詞嚟輕描淡寫，「質量」出問題乜乜乜，用嚟愚化市民<br />\n依啲手法1984都講過，用文字嚟傳播思想洗市民腦"},{"pid":"d71f87f4aebac3905bc270f3b132f2b30395ef7a","tid":1027745,"uid":155818,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"8cf94e58423ce4124e5f4475f68b6f6abdacf214","tid":1027745,"uid":838,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-02-19T04:52:30.000Z","msg":"聽啲學生講，通識科係用「質量」"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-19T06:02:27.000Z","msg":"通識科用埋&quot;素質&quot;呢個詞先UN耳<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7ba9e1452b6f815990791aa4f71ed21690c99ece","tid":1027745,"uid":14758,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-19T08:14:42.000Z","msg":"量質又有冇問題<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}